  "body": "If peers fail to decode a req/resp request we send, they should send a response chunk with an error status code and message, but they may just disconnect immediately.  This looks like the response completed successfully with no responses (e.g. no matching blocks).\n\nNeed to understand what the right behaviour is in this case.",
