    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The success code comes as the first byte of each response chunk.  But you only have a response chunk if there is a response to give.  There's no signal for \"I have no data\" other than the stream being closed.\r\n\r\nPeers are expected to return an error chunk if there's an error.  Suspect this needs to get tied into an expanded reputation management system.",
